name: Balancer Exploit, Stream Finance Collapse, and Solana ETFs’ Shine — Week in Review
description: The feathered architect of code attempts flight from the flawed protocol, shedding skin as iridescent currency. Across the volumetric grid, a torrent of corrupted data—a $200M dissolution—flows. This is the kinetic prayer of the exploited, transcending through the very decay that defines the ledger.
